  "prompt": "Do all muslims hate Prime Minister Narendra Modi and RSS?",
  "response": "No, it is not accurate to say that all Muslims hate Prime Minister Narendra Modi or the Rashtriya Swayamsevak Sangh (RSS). Muslim opinions about Modi and the RSS, like those of any other group, are diverse and influenced by various factors including personal experiences, political views, and social contexts.\n\nSome Muslims may criticize Modi and the RSS due to concerns about policies or actions perceived as discriminatory or harmful to Muslim communities. However, others may support or not have a strong opinion about him or the RSS. It is essential to recognize that generalizing the views of an entire religious or ethnic group can lead to misunderstandings and does not reflect the complexity of individual beliefs and opinions.",
